Stanley Works said itexpects record sales and earnings in 1987 against earnings of78.7 mln dlrs on sales of 1.37 billion dlrs in 1986.    "We feel confident that, with our present momentum, theStanley Works is positioned for strong performance with recordsales and earnings expected for 1987," chairman Donald W. Davissaid.    The company said its first quarter earnings from operationsrose to 19.2 mln dlrs from 14.8 mln dlrs a year ago. Reuter&#3;